articles.title: LIVE: F1 2023 Saudi Arabian Grand Prix Free Practice 2 - Racingnews365.com
articles.description: Follow the reaction to the F1 free practice day for the Saudi Arabian GP live. Keep up to date with everything that happens during FP2  and afterwards at the Jeddah Corniche Circuit.
articles.content:
Formula 1 returns to action this weekend with the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix, marking the second round of a 23-race calendar in 2023.
Max Verstappen set the pace in Friday's opening practice session. … [+374 chars]
